videos.description: Michigan State's Nick Ward leaves the game in the first half with an apparent right ankle injury.
videos.headline: Ward leaves game with non-contact injury

videos.description: Cassius Winston sends it inside to Xavier Tillman who quickly flips it to a cutting Kenny Goins who destroys the rim.
videos.headline: Tillman sends nice touch pass to Goins for dunk

videos.description: Michigan State's Cassius Winston goes on a hot streak scoring 9 points in a minute with three 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Winston nails three triples in a row
